title: Prada Large Galleria Bag
description: Prada large Galleria 2way bag in pink Saffiano leather. Featuring gold-toned hardware, dual leather handles, two external zipper pockets, and snap closures on sides. The top opens to a pink logo-print nylon interior with zip & patch pockets. Approximate dimensions: 34cm(Base-L) x 24cm(H) x 15cm(D), handle drop 13cm, detachable and adjustable shoulder strap, 59cm. Accompanied by Prada detachable clochette, keyring, receipt, certificate card (dated 30/07/2014), dustbag & box. (Pre-owned)
